OL,3,C'Wild West': MP calls for more
OL,4,Cregulation of Borders Energy projects
OL,6,FThe MP for the Borders has presented a
OL,7,Fbill in Parliament to regulate what he
OL,8,Fdescribes as a 'wild west' of energy
OL,9,Fprojects in the area.
OL,11,FJohn Lamont has proposed a new
OL,12,FGovernment agency to coordinate the
OL,13,Fplanning of infrastructure such as
OL,14,Felectricity pylons and wind farms.
OL,16,FThe Conservative MP for Berwickshire,
OL,17,FRoxburgh and Selkirk said more needs
OL,18,Fto be done to consider those in the
OL,19,Fareas where projects are developed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
