FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1784366291
OL,3,C'Wild West': MP calls for more
OL,4,Cregulation of Borders Energy projects
OL,6,FHe said: "We need to have protection
OL,7,Ffor the communities, understanding as
OL,8,Fto how many connections are going to
OL,9,Fbe allowed, so we don't get all these
OL,10,Fspeculative applications coming
OL,11,Fthrough the system. We just need
OL,12,Fcoordination."
OL,14,FIt follows numerous large rows in the
OL,15,Fsouth of Scotland over pylon plans and
OL,16,Fwind farm proposals.
OL,18,FJohn Lamont says the Government needs
OL,19,Fto understand "many communities are
OL,20,Ffeeling frustrated and under attack."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
