OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1784366291
OL,3,C'Wild West': MP calls for more
OL,4,Cregulation of Borders Energy projects
OL,6,FHe says "anything and everything is
OL,7,Fgoing on" at the moment so he argues
OL,8,Fall UK governments need to come
OL,9,Ftogether for a more coordinated
OL,10,Fapproach to planning of energy
OL,11,Fprojects.
OL,13,FHe argues it is also taking land away
OL,14,Ffrom food production.
OL,16,FLamont hopes the issue will be debated
OL,17,Fin Parliament at a later date.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
